headline: Expedia Stock (EXPE) Triggers Bullish Reversal Pattern with $200 Price Target in Sight
summary: As a business tied to consumer sentiment, travel fare aggregator and metasearch engine Expedia Group (EXPE) struggled in the new year for understandable reasons. Thanks to President Donald Trump’s aggressive trade policies, the usual economic world order has been rattled, causing great concern among both households and businesses. At the same time, evidence is emerging that EXPE stock could see a sentiment reversal. Ultimately, I am bullish on Expedia for both fundamental and technical reasons.
